SET retry TO 0
LABEL restart
WAIT 5
IF retry >= 5 THEN
    SET Process TO $'''Fail'''
    GOTO 'end'
END
SET Process TO $'''Checking image - video'''
IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['CameraClose']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
    SET Process TO $'''Opening video'''
    UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['Window \'会中主窗口\'']['Group \'QWidget\''] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: -113 OffsetY: -3
        ON ERROR

        END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{LMenu}({V})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['CameraOpen']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
        SET Process TO $'''Done'''
        GOTO 'end'
    ELSE
        Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: retry IncrementValue: 1
        SET Process TO $'''Fail - trying [%retry%]'''
        GOTO restart
    END
ELSE
    IF (System.IfProcess.ProcessIsNotRunning ProcessName: $'''wemeetapp''') THEN
        SET Process TO $'''The app isn\'t running! Starting it'''
        CALL Start
    ELSE
        GOTO 'end'
    END
END
LABEL 'end'
SET Process TO $'''Done'''
WAIT 55
